{"tid":2321970,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"譚文豪學做廚、洗埋碗 … 我想起蘇軍入侵捷克","createTime":"2020-12-12T02:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T15:23:34.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f0c0142a54dbc1d1bf4bd92b6c6f56613ed5a61a","tid":2321970,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:55:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E8%AD%9A%E6%96%87%E8%B1%AA%E5%AD%B8%E5%81%9A%E5%BB%9A-%E6%B4%97%E5%9F%8B%E7%A2%97-%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E8%B5%B7%E8%98%87%E8%BB%8D%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5%E6%8D%B7%E5%85%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25AD%259A%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25BB%259A-%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%259F%258B%25E7%25A2%2597-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2583%25B3%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%2598%2587%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%258D%25B7%25E5%2585%258B%2F&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=b2ea4c42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25AD%259A%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25BB%259A-%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%259F%258B%25E7%25A2%2597-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2583%25B3%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%2598%2587%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%258D%25B7%25E5%2585%258B%2F&h=b9a8fa9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E8%AD%9A%E6%96%87%E8%B1%AA%E5%AD%B8%E5%81%9A%E5%BB%9A-%E6%B4%97%E5%9F%8B%E7%A2%97-%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E8%B5%B7%E8%98%87%E8%BB%8D%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5%E6%8D%B7%E5%85%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n見到飛機師譚文豪去咗開茶餐廳、學做廚、洗埋碗，竟然令我想起喺我出生果年，蘇軍入侵捷克。<br />\n<br />\n當年蘇聯出動 40 萬士兵、6,000 輛坦克入侵捷克，鎮壓當年「布拉格之春」民主運動，面對蘇聯嘅軍事鎮壓，捷克人無力抵抗，部份捷克人選擇逃離捷克，大部分留下嘅捷克人，喺極權治下，不能說真話，每天都要面對荒誕離奇嘅事。<br />\n<br />\nMilan Kundera 寫嘅 Unbearable Lightness of Being 就係以呢個時代作為背景，故事後來拍成電影《布拉格之戀》，電影主角 Tomas 係腦科醫生，喺蘇軍入侵捷克之後，因為唔肯為政權塗脂抹粉，唔肯跟隨大家講大話，亦唔願意離開自己嘅故鄉，結果，不單止唔能夠再行醫，而且要做清潔工人、以抹窗為生。<br />\n<br />\n直到我 21 歲果年，即係蘇軍入侵捷克 21 年後，亦係中共鎮壓 89 民運果一年，柏林圍牆終於倒下，捷克人捱過漫長黑夜，終於建立一個民主自由嘅國家，那已經是 21 年後的事，喺呢 21 年，有多少捷克人喺極權治下，為了追求一個更美好的社會而付出巨大的代價、經歷了多少的荒謬。<br />\n<br />\n喺極權治下，只會有更多荒誕、扭曲人性嘅悲劇出現，願天佑我城、天佑香港人。<br />\n<br />\n（​原文無題，題為編輯所擬）<br />\n<br />\n作者facebook"},{"pid":"e636a332a58b43a8e62813e013f002b00b2e6313","tid":2321970,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445834263d6e656158836f918a8bb699542d2b35","tid":2321970,"uid":94982,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飛機師出國做飛機師啦"},{"pid":"0fa85085ef316202bf3a579179443d281b19d53d","tid":2321970,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T07:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16858c3e3c76837cbe0954549d9c528ac3fe52af","tid":2321970,"uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:41:51.000Z","msg":"香港人唔知要等幾多個21年先得"},{"pid":"6c2368f23553d345938d2bb040eec9d46338279b","tid":2321970,"uid":215621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T15:23:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}